msgid "Cache level at which irqbalance partitions cache domains."
msgstr "Leibhéal taisce ag a ndéanann irqbalance landairí taisce."

msgid "Deepest cache"
msgstr "Taisce is doimhne"

msgid "Enable"
msgstr "Cumasaigh"

msgid "Exclude CPUs"
msgstr "Fág LAPanna as an áireamh"

msgid "Exclude IRQs"
msgstr "Fág IRQanna san áireamh"

msgid "General settings"
msgstr "Socruithe ginearálta"

msgid "Grant UCI access for luci-app-irqbalance"
msgstr "Deonaigh rochtain UCI ar luci-app-irqbalance"

msgid "Interval"
msgstr "Eatramh"

msgid "Invalid"
msgstr "Neamhbhailí"

msgid ""
"List of CPUs to ignore, can be an integer or integers separated by commas."
msgstr ""
"Liosta de na LAPanna le neamhaird a dhéanamh, is féidir a bheith ina "
"slánuimhir nó slánuimhreacha scartha le camóga."

msgid "List of IRQs to ignore."
msgstr "Liosta de IRQanna le neamhaird a dhéanamh."

msgid "Loading..."
msgstr "Á lódáil..."

msgid "NOT RUNNING"
msgstr "NÍ RÚCHÁN"

msgid "RUNNING"
msgstr "REATHA"

msgid "Show debug output"
msgstr "Taispeáin aschur dífhabhtaithe"

msgid "Show debug output in system log."
msgstr "Taispeáin aschur dífhabhtaithe i loga an chórais."

msgid "Snapshot of current IRQs"
msgstr "Léiriú ar IRQanna reatha"

msgid ""
"The purpose of irqbalance is to distribute hardware interrupts across "
"processors/cores on a multiprocessor/multicore system in order to increase "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Is é cuspóir irqbalance ná idirbhriseadh crua-earraí a dháileadh ar "
"phróiseálaithe/croíláir ar chóras ilphróiseálaí/ilchórais chun feidhmíocht a "
"mhéadú."

msgid "Valid values: %s."
msgstr "Luachanna bailí: %s."

msgid "Value in seconds."
msgstr "Luach i soicindí."

msgid "irqbalance"
msgstr "irqbalance"
